01:40:49.030 --> 01:40:52.190
And so transgressing
that, there's

01:40:52.190 --> 01:40:54.730
a lot more punishment
that men face.

01:40:54.730 --> 01:40:58.260
And so I think that's also
true for fatherhood probably

01:40:58.260 --> 01:41:02.500
