01:41:12.200 --> 01:41:15.170
This is not a fairness issue.

01:41:15.170 --> 01:41:17.130
It's not a politeness.

01:41:17.130 --> 01:41:21.500
This is a business issue,
diversity of all types.

01:41:21.500 --> 01:41:25.360
Gender diversity, racial
and ethnicity-- we have to,

01:41:25.360 --> 01:41:26.750
as business leaders, do that.

01:41:26.750 --> 01:41:30.564
And I think that case has not
been sufficiently persuasively

01:41:30.564 --> 01:41:31.105
communicated.

01:41:33.930 --> 01:41:34.640
-Excellent.

